props.name: id
props.desc:
The DomQuery path relative from the record element to the element that contains
a record identifier value.

props.name: record
props.desc: The DomQuery path to the repeated element which contains record information.

props.name: success
props.desc: The DomQuery path to the success attribute used by forms.

props.name: totalRecords
props.desc:
The DomQuery path from which to retrieve the total number of records
in the dataset. This is only needed if the whole dataset is not passed in one go, but is being
paged from the remote server.
